reviewText: all are good movies well acted the mermaid flick I hunted for and gave up and here it is love it

A worthwhile value pack of creature features with Anaconda being an instant cult classic. Dark Water is a worthy watch, a nice little thriller with a bit of drag in its structure, that features a killer croc. Even Red Water is decent action SyFy fare that has sharks amok up a fresh water river inlet. Lou Diamond Phillips elevates this ride. The She Creature copy unfortunately was a lackluster transfer. Its otherwise pretty decent too and features some nice Stan Winston practical effects of a killer mermaid. A solid 4 stars for this package deal. At $5 you cant beat the price.
Buying this dvd set is cheaper than just buying Anaconda by itself. Great deal, even though the other 3 movies are not that great. It is a good and cheap way of completing your Anaconda Collection.
